#: ../../source/unit/envpro.rst:3 bb9fca3459da4e2b9b1dbecce4dbcb9b
msgid "ENVPRO Unit"
msgstr "ENVPRO Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/envpro.rst:7 26410409bc0f4c3893a3bf13a42b1800
msgid ""
"ENV Pro Unit is an environmental sensor that utilizes the BME688 sensor "
"solution, supporting the measurement of various environmental parameters "
"such as volatile organic compounds (VOCs), indoor air quality (IAQ), "
"temperature, humidity, and atmospheric pressure. It features a compact "
"size, wide operating range, simple communication interface (I2C), "
"excellent performance, and low power consumption, making it suitable for "
"weather stations, indoor environmental monitoring, and air quality "
"detection applications."
msgstr ""
"ENV Pro Unit 是一款环境传感器，采用 BME688 "
"传感器方案，支持测量多种环境参数，例如挥发性有机化合物（VOCs）、室内空气质量（IAQ）、温度、湿度和大气压。其具有体积小、工作范围宽、通信接口简单（I2C）、性能优异以及低功耗等特点，适用于气象站、室内环境监测和空气质量检测等应用场景。"

